snippet.title: #75 - Rob Squad Reactions to Sound of Silence - With Rob and Amber
snippet.description:
Rob and Amber are the Dynamic Duo who make up the Rob Squad Reactions team. They listen to all types of music that they've never heard before and react to it. They have a vibe about them that is so genuine and positive that you can't help but smile when watching their videos.
If you enjoy them as much as I do be sure to check them out on Youtube and subscribe to their channel, The Rob Squad Reactions. You'll be happy you did.
